snippet.title: Evolution Dino Dudes - Atari Jaguar
snippet.description:
Evolution Dino Dudes is sort of a puzzle game, but with little prehistoric men!
I remember having & playing this game when I first got a Jaguar, which was around 13 or 14 years ago. I loved it then and it's still a great game.
Your cavemen can have different abilities as you progress and acquire different tools for use in your crusade.
This video only shows the first 2 levels, but further on you can even discover.... THE WHEEEEEL!!!
:o
